# Python package manager lockfiles. Ignored by default — but core-api commits
# its lock (CAURA-000 pilot): its Dockerfile installs FROZEN from uv.lock so the
# deployed image can't silently float to a new release (a lock-less pip install
# floated to FastAPI 0.137 and crashed prod 2026-06-14). The other services stay
# lock-less until the pilot is rolled out to them.
**/uv.lock
!core-api/uv.lock
